<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:44">Membership Levels</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:40">
	Annual Membership ($85.00 per fiscal year)
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:3:90">
	Lifetime Membership ($1,000)
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:4:45">
	Annual membership is from Oct 1st – Sept 30th (fiscal year). If the joining date is after July 1, 2026, membership payment will cover the following fiscal year (Oct 1, 2026 - Sept 30, 2027)
</p>
<hr data-zesty-id="design:design:horizontalrule:5:65">
<h6 style="text-align:center;" id="form" data-zesty-id="content:text:6:97">Join or Renew Membership Now</h6>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:7:51">
	Complete the form below to renew your current membership, or apply for new membership
</p>
<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:8:62">Membership Payment</h6>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:56">You can pay your Member Dues through the following options:</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:34"><strong>1) Cash or check in person</strong></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:11:90">
	You can also mail membership checks addressed to SAWA, 501 Rutherford St., Greenville, SC 29609.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:12:79">
	<strong>2) Pay online through the button below</strong>
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:13:45">
	<em>(Please be sure to type in the correct payment amount, and then select the membership type in the drop-down box)</em>
</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:14:5"><a href="https://fundraise.givesmart.com/form/jiuzcg?vid=1i9w6c" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Pay Online</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:15:47"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:16:43">
	<strong>3) Venmo through the button below</strong>
</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:17:13"><a href="https://venmo.com/sawagvl" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Venmo @SAWAGVL</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:18:37"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:20:57">
	If you'd rather download the SAWA membership or renewal forms, click the buttons below. You can also click the button to gift a membership to someone else.&nbsp;
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:21:28"></div>
